 bodies of Mrs. <PERSON> Cucci </PERSON> and Mrs. <PERSON> Chacon </PERSON> were lying in state in a <LOCATION> Cuzco </LOCATION> municipal building. Doctors said the women appeared to have died from skull fractures. The Cuccis were visiting to celebrate a sister city agreement between <LOCATION> Jersey </LOCATION> <LOCATION> City </LOCATION> and <LOCATION> Cuzco </LOCATION>. <LOCATION> Cuzco </LOCATION> is a tourist area about 355 miles southeast of <LOCATION> Lima </LOCATION>. Six other people were on the vehicle but did not suffer serious injuries.
