joint mission, said there has been an evolution of sorts in the astronaut corps, with a greater diversity of skills and backgrounds. <PERSON> Hee </PERSON> said he expects even more diversity in the future. `` Space is like the American West, the Arctic or <LOCATION> Antarctica </LOCATION>. It's a new locality where you can do all kinds of different things,'' <PERSON> Brand </PERSON> said
